\title{mockallofus: A Local Mock Database for Developing All of Us Analyses}
\description{
Builds a local DuckDB database with fully synthetic data that mirrors the table and column structure of the All of Us Research Program Curated Data Repository (OMOP CDM plus All of Us extensions). Lets users develop and test 'allofus' package analysis code locally, without the paid Researcher Workbench. The synthetic data is randomly generated and does not reflect real All of Us data. The same analysis code is intended to run against the mock database locally and against the real data on the Workbench, with a small set of clearly-documented exceptions.
